A '''nullification chamber''' was a structure that placed persons into [[Suspended animation/Legends|suspended animation]]. The exact mechanism was unknown, but as soon as an organism entered the chamber it was put into stasis. The [[Hall of Satabs]] was a nullification chamber that was used to prevent the ultimate effects of the [[shadeshine]].

